ion: none><u>Contact Samadhi</u></font></td></tr></table></span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/22/02 8:06:07 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1153.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: point?</span><hr size=1> You can kill all 4 warders, but one always has to be up. For example, one clearing you can kill 1, 2, and 3, and leave the 4th up. The next clearing, you can kill 1, 2, and 4, and leave the 3rd up. As long as 1 warder is up, the sleeper is not awakened. As soon as all warders are dead however, he is released. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ujoshm789.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Joshm789</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/22/02 9:09:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1153.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://forum.square-x.com/avatars/final_fantasy_viii_-_squall_2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: point?</span><hr size=1> Welcome to all servers where the sleeper is awake.  If you haven't been to Tholuxe Paells board, try www.tholuxe.com =)<br>
<br>
We have at least Kupo Flux vs. Paradigm Nocturne flame going about ST, and how a KF member is ebaying SOD's and the PN people are buying them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uryll.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ryll</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/22/02 10:41:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1153.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: point?</span><hr size=1> Oddly enough, the fact that after the first awakening it was discovered that this did NOTHING good for the server, or the guild/group that awakened it... it is surprising to me that anyone, let alone everyone, has tried to awaken the sleeper. There is no reward for waking the sleeper, the loot or combat in ST does not improve, nor does it anywhere else. <br>
<br>
It is just a poorly conceived and implemented content that allows the earliest to a zone to get the best items, and those that struggle and lag behind to miss out. <br>
<br>
This should have opened a new, better zone, or released stronger, better treasure critters in ST, imo... but alas, it is just a zone to work to get into, so that you can farm it first, and the ruin it for others... lame.<br>
<br>
Ryll <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uclaudshadowflare.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ClaudShadowflare</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/23/02 1:00:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1153.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ST</span><hr size=1> Hell, VI's even gone on record saying Sleepers' Tomb was a really big fucking mistake on their part, but words that are more appropriate for explaining it to players you wish to maintain subscriptions.<br>
