Kinda disappointing though how this encounter was used as a form of revenge, and at the expense of other guilds not involved in this feud.<br>
<br>
But it's REALLY gay how so many people who had nothing to do with Sleepers Tomb, and wouldn't for some time to come, jumped up in arms about this.  Everyone across the server had expected him to die soon; hell, we are Xegony, most of us are assholes, someone was bound to do it just because they could.  I just wish people could shut up for more than 5 minutes between every /ooc, /shout, /gui (not like we're anywhere near ST... couple have keys but we didn't get the keys for them), or message to the buysell channel about the sleeper.  My god, I am so fucking sick of the sleeper already.  &quot;Is anything new with the SLEEPER?&quot;  &quot;Can you believe what happened with the SLEEPER?&quot;  &quot;Is the SLEEPER coming back?&quot;  &quot;Hey Claud, what do you think about the SLEEPER?&quot;<br>
