59.6 Evoker of Xegony<br>
Big Gay Pink Dragon Hater <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugemlin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gemlin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/23/02 5:07:39 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1153.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ST</span><hr size=1> So what if someone woke the sleeper. Primals drop off the named Golems and drop what appears more frequently.<br>
<br>
